Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.23,0:00:27.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天有很多甜食哟
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.08,0:00:30.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦 不全是苦的么
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.00,0:00:47.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,犯那种错的话可真是没办法啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.69,0:00:51.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,克鲁那产的哈齐玛
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.87,0:00:55.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还有啊 妈妈 我可是做得最棒的哟
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.76,0:00:57.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下次给你看看
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.52,0:01:02.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嫁给我吧！
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.90,0:01:08.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,莱卡特 王都你是第一次来吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.82,0:01:11.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是 小时候来过一次
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.72,0:01:13.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被老爸带着来的
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.56,0:01:16.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,莱卡特
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.33,0:01:18.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,莱卡特
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.46,0:01:20.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能动吗
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.18,0:01:46.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,够了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.82,0:01:50.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,撤退
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.75,0:02:06.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,莱卡特 你还好吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.91,0:02:10.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 大叔
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.73,0:02:20.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你说什么 我听不到
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.88,0:02:24.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯？ 我们回毗傩天了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.85,0:02:27.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,三台在后方负责警戒和侦查
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.15,0:02:28.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别被人发现了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.07,0:02:28.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.98,0:02:38.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,北方有难民过来
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.75,0:02:39.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,进行引导工作
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.58,0:02:42.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,避难船回来之前待命
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.52,0:02:44.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,保护军队生活用品的运送
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.13,0:02:47.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,中部避难所发生事故
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.94,0:02:50.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,民间的代表不是应该已经定下来了么
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.38,0:02:52.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,码头的收容准备工作怎样了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.00,0:02:54.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,霍兹尔陛下在哪
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.09,0:02:56.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,让运输车过来
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.93,0:02:58.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在公园广场集合
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.15,0:03:00.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,霍兹尔陛下也不知哪去了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.36,0:03:03.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,向东环状外门移动
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.17,0:03:08.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,诶 卫兵到底在搞什么
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.80,0:03:48.48,OPJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,400)}特別なものは何もないけど
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.53,0:04:01.93,OPJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,400)}その手に掴むには　充分すぎる愛を
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.17,0:04:16.19,OPJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,400)}信じるものを持っている者は
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.82,0:04:31.34,OPJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,400)}揺るぎない愛の為に貫く想いを
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.42,0:04:39.95,OPJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,400)}運命に立ち向かえるなら
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.47,0:04:49.60,OPJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,800)}この全て懸ける想いでゆく
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.80,0:03:48.48,OPCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,400)}虽无甚特别之物
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.53,0:04:01.93,OPCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,400)}却有爱满溢双手
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.17,0:04:16.19,OPCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,400)}心有所信之人
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.82,0:04:31.34,OPCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,400)}倾注思念 只为不渝大爱
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.42,0:04:39.95,OPCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,400)}若注定直面命运
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.47,0:04:49.60,OPCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,800)}唯有付出一切 勇往直前
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.53,0:05:11.41,Title,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(1000,1000}恸哭之城
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.19,0:05:24.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,难得你会迟到啊 伊奥上校
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.13,0:05:28.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,尼克战死了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.54,0:05:29.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.27,0:05:34.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,将军 这种大风天气下增援部队都迟到了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.99,0:05:39.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,无所谓 完全不影响我们的计划
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.30,0:05:43.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等他们到的时候战斗已经结束了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.78,0:05:46.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就让我们在被占领的毗傩天欢迎他们吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.96,0:05:48.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.63,0:05:52.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,瓦尔基里斯部队的一位名叫克莱欧的士兵
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.65,0:05:54.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,据说一直被扣押在毗傩天
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.47,0:05:57.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她是萨布拉夫家的千金
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.72,0:05:59.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然消息不一定可靠…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.71,0:06:01.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我前去确认下
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.68,0:06:03.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真有此事的话便把她救出来
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.37,0:06:08.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,接下来我们要进攻王宫 攻陷毗傩天
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.40,0:06:16.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果能救出这位小姐 确实能在国内成为一段佳话
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.44,0:06:18.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但这与我毫无关系
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.03,0:06:19.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.68,0:06:24.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,接下来向毗傩天进发
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.82,0:06:27.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,全员准备出击
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.28,0:06:29.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是 遵命
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.13,0:06:37.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么在毗傩天的王宫见吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.07,0:06:38.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.89,0:06:49.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,出击
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.83,0:07:18.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.99,0:07:20.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.43,0:07:29.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,娜尔维他们呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.59,0:07:31.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没看到吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.20,0:07:36.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,第一个找到的是你
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.81,0:07:40.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他们的大部队开始行动了 有90台机体
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.86,0:07:43.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,波尔库斯准备趁着天黑一口气攻过来
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.56,0:07:46.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们也不能在这过多停留了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.32,0:07:48.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没问题吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.67,0:07:49.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是 没问题
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.91,0:07:51.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好 全员登机
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.97,0:07:52.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.47,0:07:58.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,莱卡特
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.03,0:08:00.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.48,0:08:05.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.22,0:08:08.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,洛金 洛金
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.09,0:08:10.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,洛金 洛金
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.07,0:08:15.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你还活着啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.94,0:08:21.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,娜尔维 怎么了 军服破破烂烂的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.75,0:08:28.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,奈尔哥 不会是幽灵吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.80,0:08:32.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 我自己都觉得不可思议
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.26,0:08:34.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过确实还能动
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.77,0:08:41.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在怎么办
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.12,0:08:44.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿特内斯大部队应该正前往毗傩天
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.13,0:08:47.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们得想办法先到一步进行补给
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.65,0:08:51.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想办法？ 难道要用这法布尼尔跑一晚上？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.46,0:08:54.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,半路遇到敌人怎么办
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.68,0:08:57.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那正好 就当武器的补给了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.56,0:08:58.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.45,0:09:00.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,趁他们不注意偷袭他们就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.47,0:09:04.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他们也想不到有人会用这台法布尼尔进攻吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.95,0:09:17.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,向西琼大人报告 物资已经运达
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.65,0:09:19.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,让难民上船吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.72,0:09:21.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,总比空手回去强多了是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.87,0:09:26.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,运来的石英比克里修那的硬度更高
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.51,0:09:31.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请注意一下 打磨机可能会折断
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.29,0:09:32.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.11,0:09:34.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且 不能花太长时间
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.71,0:09:35.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.61,0:09:42.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我该怎么办啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.86,0:09:44.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,古拉姆
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.05,0:09:54.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,莱卡特呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.45,0:09:58.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,报告说他已经和巴尔德将军汇合 向这边赶来
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.27,0:10:00.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,娜尔维他们呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.45,0:10:02.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下落不明
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.51,0:10:06.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,剩下的市民中20%可以收容在王城
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.30,0:10:09.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是从北方避难者的人数来看…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.16,0:10:11.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,正在确保登船工作顺利进行
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.35,0:10:13.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,水和粮食的储备呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.41,0:10:15.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大概能维持2个月
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.37,0:10:20.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 有了这些就能争取到和欧兰德的交涉时间了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.14,0:10:25.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在说什么 那个波尔库斯将军正在向这大举进攻啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.23,0:10:29.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,恐怕明早就到了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.43,0:10:34.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,守备的格雷姆有60台 要是被那个人突破防线的话…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.06,0:10:35.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,近卫大队长
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.62,0:10:39.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,情况我已经清楚了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.48,0:10:47.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,终究没法…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.57,0:10:50.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抵抗命运吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.28,0:11:17.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们抢在波尔库斯前到达王都的几率很小
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.89,0:11:19.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要做好没有补给就开始战斗的准备
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.87,0:11:20.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明白
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.27,0:11:26.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,莱卡特 再次启动帝尔锋之前
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.40,0:11:28.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有遭遇敌人的危险
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.80,0:11:31.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,莱卡特
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.88,0:11:34.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 我藏好了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.57,0:11:38.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,找个地方把我放下来吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.20,0:12:32.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太好了 没想到能得到这么大块的石英
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.21,0:12:34.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小菜一碟
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.29,0:12:38.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过对这打磨机来说负担太好像重了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.85,0:12:42.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 我并不是反对王妃大人的计划
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.32,0:12:43.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然不能用作最后工序
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.76,0:12:46.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果用于最初打孔的话 我有更好的工具
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.52,0:12:49.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样一来还能节省时间
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.39,0:12:51.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是现在才开始…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.04,0:12:54.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的船上准备了各种东西
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.85,0:12:56.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,应有尽有
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.71,0:13:05.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来了 估计有90台
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.48,0:13:10.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,波尔库斯 竟公然从正面攻来
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.87,0:13:13.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,巴尔德将军没能赶上吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.90,0:13:14.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,敌袭！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.41,0:13:17.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在开始一级防御战
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.89,0:13:26.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,敌袭 开始一级防御战
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.02,0:13:28.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一号 第一种配备
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.93,0:13:32.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,东外门以及东门配备完成
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.15,0:13:35.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,绝对不能让他们进入王都
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.30,0:13:35.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.45,0:13:37.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,敌人来了 快点
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.79,0:13:51.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,新型机吗 已经追上来了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.57,0:13:57.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,巴蒂斯 王都好像想让我们吃个闭门羹呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.51,0:13:59.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,敲敲门让他们放我们进去访问下吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.19,0:14:01.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明白
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.81,0:14:03.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,各队 散开
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.69,0:14:04.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明白
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.56,0:14:08.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么各位 化身野兽吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.03,0:14:27.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,西面27台 东面18台 部队已经散开
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.54,0:14:31.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,无论如何都要从正面攻来么
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.59,0:14:37.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,射击
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.92,0:14:51.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,陛下 请去避难吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.69,0:14:55.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 市民都避难了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.60,0:14:56.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早就去了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.96,0:14:57.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,难民呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.65,0:14:59.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到达这里的就是全部了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.50,0:15:03.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,事到如今已经没法接近毗傩天了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.28,0:15:09.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为了从陆路迂回到库恩鲁已经派出了救援队 可是…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.61,0:15:13.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么样
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.17,0:15:15.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好厉害
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.17,0:15:17.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已经可以替换了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.06,0:15:19.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,韧带准备好了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.94,0:15:55.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,绝佳的防御位置么
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.63,0:15:57.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,先去把门打开
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.60,0:16:12.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,莱特
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.67,0:16:17.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,巴蒂斯将军已经和艾尔特密斯·改部队汇合了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.79,0:16:19.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我可是专攻远程射击的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.07,0:16:23.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,干的漂亮
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.97,0:16:36.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如此寒酸的欢迎啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.44,0:16:50.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,波尔库斯
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.57,0:16:56.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,挺勇猛的嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.46,0:17:04.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,走 进去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.41,0:17:10.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别让他们进去
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.92,0:17:19.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,进入第二防御态势 把他们封锁在北门内
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.06,0:17:35.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然在这 和西琼大人推断的一样
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.96,0:17:38.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样就行了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.87,0:17:40.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,连接韧带
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.55,0:17:42.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,强化连接的准备好了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.71,0:17:46.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要让那一大捆韧带动起来吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.95,0:17:49.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是让韧带动起来
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.02,0:17:53.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们需要的是能承受那份重量的强度和韧度
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.69,0:17:56.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,连接用的韧带怎么办
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.69,0:18:00.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,稍等一下 我马上去拿
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.77,0:18:02.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,西琼大人 等等
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.00,0:18:07.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,瞄准很精确啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.81,0:18:23.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不会再让你们向前一步了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.22,0:18:32.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不会就想凭这么点人来阻止我们的突破吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.10,0:18:40.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哼 要被东门那边占了先机么
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.49,0:18:50.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去确保北门到这里的移动通路
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.69,0:18:51.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,遵命
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.87,0:18:56.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我来把他们全部击坠
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.22,0:18:58.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,莱特
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.20,0:19:11.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,新型的改良机种吗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.99,0:19:32.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是巴尔德将军吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.51,0:19:36.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没想到会从背后过来呢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.10,0:19:40.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,分别对付各自目标 祝各位成功
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.34,0:19:41.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,遵命
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.37,0:20:03.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,西琼大人
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.55,0:20:04.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,稍等一下
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.73,0:20:24.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,坐床上去
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.94,0:20:25.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快点
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.27,0:20:31.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请进
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.27,0:20:35.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个和这个 快点
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.31,0:20:36.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,负责看守的两位也来帮忙
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.35,0:20:38.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但 但是
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.71,0:20:40.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快点 没时间了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.63,0:20:41.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.53,0:20:42.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个也拜托了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.76,0:20:44.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别弄坏了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.27,0:20:45.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.15,0:20:47.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我很快就来
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.29,0:20:55.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可以了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.99,0:21:02.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我正在制造能打败你们国家格雷姆的武器
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.49,0:21:07.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是只有帝尔锋能用
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.99,0:21:10.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等莱卡特回来就交给他
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.00,0:21:14.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然还没有收到他回来的消息
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.94,0:21:18.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但他一定会回来的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.95,0:21:20.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们约好的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.80,0:21:26.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你平安回来的话 我就不生气了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.96,0:21:33.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 知道啦
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.00,0:21:37.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,克莱欧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.44,0:21:43.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其实我也想和你做个约定
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.12,0:21:46.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.33,0:21:49.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,西琼姐
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.61,0:22:00.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,帝尔
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.75,0:22:05.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,差不多要出发了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:23:16.97,0:23:18.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们在干什么
Dialogue: 0,0:23:18.18,0:23:21.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别让他们过去 开火啊
Dialogue: 0,0:23:22.32,0:23:23.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可恶
Dialogue: 0,0:23:51.10,0:23:53.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不愧是巴尔德将军
Dialogue: 0,0:23:55.27,0:23:57.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,居然能把我们挡在这里
Dialogue: 0,0:23:57.62,0:23:59.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是时间紧迫
Dialogue: 0,0:24:02.59,0:24:04.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,容我们先走一步了
Dialogue: 0,0:24:06.49,0:24:10.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看到那些村民 你是怎么想的
Dialogue: 0,0:24:11.25,0:24:12.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我该怎么办
Dialogue: 0,0:24:12.39,0:24:14.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,克里修那这个国家已经注定要灭亡了
Dialogue: 0,0:24:14.86,0:24:16.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们这帮蛮族
Dialogue: 0,0:24:16.66,0:24:19.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是不是觉得现在是在打仗所以没办法
Dialogue: 0,0:24:19.56,0:24:21.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别人的死给你的担子太重了
Dialogue: 0,0:24:21.91,0:24:23.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你没有责任
Dialogue: 0,0:24:33.95,0:24:34.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,帝尔
Dialogue: 0,0:24:54.87,0:24:56.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是悲哀啊
Dialogue: 0,0:24:56.13,0:24:59.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,即使知道结果如何 也不得不竭尽全力
Dialogue: 0,0:25:24.86,0:25:27.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们也利用建筑物阴影的掩蔽继续前进
Dialogue: 0,0:25:27.61,0:25:28.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,迅速前往会合地点
Dialogue: 0,0:25:29.07,0:25:29.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,伊奥上校
Dialogue: 0,0:25:30.35,0:25:32.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,莱特 继续后方掩护
Dialogue: 0,0:25:35.72,0:25:36.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好 前进
Dialogue: 0,0:25:37.01,0:25:37.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,上校
Dialogue: 0,0:25:40.47,0:25:42.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我来掩护上校
Dialogue: 0,0:25:42.74,0:25:44.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,既然比预定提前到了这里
Dialogue: 0,0:25:45.08,0:25:46.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,之后就没问题了
Dialogue: 0,0:25:46.73,0:25:48.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,交给你了 莱特
Dialogue: 0,0:25:48.61,0:25:49.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,上校
Dialogue: 0,0:25:52.81,0:25:55.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,波尔库斯
Dialogue: 0,0:26:01.18,0:26:02.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你好像还不明白
Dialogue: 0,0:26:03.44,0:26:06.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,从你无法守护身后王宫的那一刻起
Dialogue: 0,0:26:06.18,0:26:07.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你就已经有辱使命了
Dialogue: 0,0:26:12.47,0:26:13.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,波尔库斯
Dialogue: 0,0:26:43.82,0:26:45.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,莱 莱卡特
Dialogue: 0,0:26:50.41,0:26:51.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是黑银啊
Dialogue: 0,0:26:52.46,0:26:55.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还没看你用过弹射枪啊
Dialogue: 0,0:26:58.97,0:27:00.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,波尔库斯
Dialogue: 0,0:27:00.67,0:27:03.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是未知格雷姆的特性么
Dialogue: 0,0:27:04.13,0:27:06.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还是只是驾驶员的问题呢
Dialogue: 0,0:27:07.59,0:27:08.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,波尔库斯
Dialogue: 0,0:27:09.29,0:27:13.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,先把王宫打下来 然后再慢慢确认吧
Dialogue: 0,0:27:17.86,0:27:19.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请调整到完全张紧的状态
Dialogue: 0,0:27:20.17,0:27:21.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,西琼大人 请您退后
Dialogue: 0,0:27:21.99,0:27:22.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再紧一点
Dialogue: 0,0:27:22.93,0:27:23.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是来真的？
Dialogue: 0,0:27:23.90,0:27:26.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,西琼大人 帝尔锋已经返回了
Dialogue: 0,0:27:27.21,0:27:28.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,装甲怎么样
Dialogue: 0,0:27:28.05,0:27:31.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,多亏找到它时是在启动待机中 已经安装好了
Dialogue: 0,0:27:31.46,0:27:34.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在正在交战中 沿中央大道朝这里来了
Dialogue: 0,0:27:35.24,0:27:36.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,莱卡特
Dialogue: 0,0:27:40.12,0:27:42.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 已经开始了
Dialogue: 0,0:27:43.21,0:27:46.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,北门…被法布尼尔的残骸…
Dialogue: 0,0:27:46.91,0:27:48.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抓紧！
Dialogue: 0,0:27:56.01,0:28:00.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我可不想和赤手空拳的敌人打 那只是浪费时间
Dialogue: 0,0:28:06.37,0:28:07.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,莱卡特
Dialogue: 0,0:28:07.59,0:28:11.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还是跳得这么高啊 黑银
Dialogue: 0,0:28:11.73,0:28:13.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过还是徒劳
Dialogue: 0,0:28:36.33,0:28:39.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我在古代战争书籍中读到过
Dialogue: 0,0:28:39.51,0:28:43.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,书上说两国战到终局时会互相投石
Dialogue: 0,0:28:44.52,0:28:48.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哼哼 可没想到居然在这里也能见到啊
Dialogue: 0,0:28:56.86,0:28:59.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行 这样下去胳膊就…
Dialogue: 0,0:28:59.61,0:29:04.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个似乎也曾读到过 互殴好像也是兵法的一种
Dialogue: 0,0:29:11.97,0:29:16.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这防御不错 不过靠这个可没法保卫国家
Dialogue: 0,0:29:19.58,0:29:21.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把它们连接在一起
Dialogue: 0,0:29:22.90,0:29:26.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为了保持韧带的强度 请尽可能系紧一些
Dialogue: 0,0:29:45.27,0:29:48.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我似乎有些地方弄错了
Dialogue: 0,0:29:48.32,0:29:53.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,确实 黑银的力量与我们不可同日而语
Dialogue: 0,0:29:53.67,0:29:56.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这力量并不是来自驾驶员的
Dialogue: 0,0:29:56.48,0:30:02.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但似乎驾驶员也是和我们完全不同的异类
Dialogue: 0,0:30:03.07,0:30:07.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不会是从古代苏醒而来的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:30:07.92,0:30:11.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么办 他还有什么别的武器
Dialogue: 0,0:30:18.31,0:30:20.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,第三内门被突破了
Dialogue: 0,0:30:20.52,0:30:22.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,西侧防线交战中
Dialogue: 0,0:30:22.37,0:30:25.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,从东面进来的部队正向中央移动
Dialogue: 0,0:30:28.72,0:30:29.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我必须回去
Dialogue: 0,0:30:34.12,0:30:35.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,完全来迟了
Dialogue: 0,0:30:35.74,0:30:38.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去包抄他们 在立交桥处将敌人击溃
Dialogue: 0,0:30:38.54,0:30:40.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好 大干一场吧
Dialogue: 0,0:30:42.30,0:30:43.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好美啊
Dialogue: 0,0:30:44.07,0:30:44.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯？
Dialogue: 0,0:30:44.93,0:30:46.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,王宫在闪光
Dialogue: 0,0:30:47.99,0:30:50.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 决不让敌人靠近
Dialogue: 0,0:31:06.82,0:31:08.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看不懂
Dialogue: 0,0:31:11.63,0:31:14.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他的战术本身就让人难以理解
Dialogue: 0,0:31:14.78,0:31:16.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是在干什么…
Dialogue: 0,0:32:02.91,0:32:06.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是 就没考虑过重量的问题吗
Dialogue: 0,0:32:10.52,0:32:11.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这家伙
Dialogue: 0,0:32:16.41,0:32:18.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你想要的不是那个吧
Dialogue: 0,0:32:19.50,0:32:26.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是为什么不用弹射枪呢 石英传导没出故障啊
Dialogue: 0,0:32:28.38,0:32:32.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我见多了那些自称精英的无能者
Dialogue: 0,0:32:33.54,0:32:36.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是像这种据说以百万分之一的概率降生的家伙
Dialogue: 0,0:32:36.88,0:32:39.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我还从没见过
Dialogue: 0,0:32:40.86,0:32:44.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,居然 真的存在么
Dialogue: 0,0:32:44.90,0:32:47.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,莱卡特呢 帝尔锋在哪儿
Dialogue: 0,0:32:47.46,0:32:49.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在立交桥附近战斗中
Dialogue: 0,0:32:50.22,0:32:51.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把它搬出去
Dialogue: 0,0:32:51.27,0:32:52.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把这个？
Dialogue: 0,0:32:53.33,0:32:57.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,作为武器看起来很原始是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:32:57.56,0:33:00.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,该说是原始吗…
Dialogue: 0,0:33:00.11,0:33:04.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其实 驾驶员莱卡特·阿罗 他不能使用魔力
Dialogue: 0,0:33:04.60,0:33:05.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,诶？
Dialogue: 0,0:33:06.64,0:33:08.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是要怎样…
Dialogue: 0,0:33:08.39,0:33:13.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,帝尔锋是古代技术所制造的 操纵极其困难
Dialogue: 0,0:33:13.42,0:33:17.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是不知为何 身为无能者饱受歧视的莱卡特
Dialogue: 0,0:33:17.19,0:33:18.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只有他才能开动帝尔锋
Dialogue: 0,0:33:19.17,0:33:21.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然现在原因还不清楚
Dialogue: 0,0:33:22.41,0:33:26.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 那个驾驶员就可以使用这武器是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:33:27.67,0:33:29.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,用魔力以外的某种东西
Dialogue: 0,0:33:29.66,0:33:30.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大概
Dialogue: 0,0:33:32.26,0:33:33.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是因为他是个怪人吧
Dialogue: 0,0:33:35.56,0:33:37.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,准备就绪 帝尔锋那边呢
Dialogue: 0,0:33:37.96,0:33:41.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请把大门打开 帝尔锋那边我去说明
Dialogue: 0,0:33:44.98,0:33:46.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,西琼大人
Dialogue: 0,0:33:47.11,0:33:48.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怪人么
Dialogue: 0,0:33:48.62,0:33:49.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,向第一内门移动
Dialogue: 0,0:33:49.86,0:33:51.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快把那东西运到门那去
Dialogue: 0,0:34:05.39,0:34:07.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,无魔力者
Dialogue: 0,0:34:13.07,0:34:15.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是杰斯队的克莱欧·萨布拉夫阁下吗
Dialogue: 0,0:34:17.15,0:34:19.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是波尔库斯大队所属的伊奥
Dialogue: 0,0:34:19.47,0:34:21.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 是的 我是杰斯大人…
Dialogue: 0,0:34:21.93,0:34:23.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,瓦尔基里斯队的克莱欧
Dialogue: 0,0:34:24.06,0:34:24.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,您受伤了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:34:25.17,0:34:26.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在还没有
Dialogue: 0,0:34:27.00,0:34:28.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我一定把您送回阿特内斯
Dialogue: 0,0:34:29.40,0:34:31.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,之后就请交给我
Dialogue: 0,0:34:31.65,0:34:33.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,万分感谢
Dialogue: 0,0:34:53.10,0:34:56.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再见了 西琼姐
Dialogue: 0,0:35:00.04,0:35:02.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是上次那家伙  看我收拾你
Dialogue: 0,0:35:07.11,0:35:09.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,密密麻麻地都钻进来了
Dialogue: 0,0:35:27.43,0:35:31.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很遗憾 这韧带事到如今己经毫无用处了
Dialogue: 0,0:35:33.14,0:35:33.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,莱卡特
Dialogue: 0,0:35:41.74,0:35:42.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,西琼
Dialogue: 0,0:35:44.40,0:35:45.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,接着
Dialogue: 0,0:35:46.00,0:35:48.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,接着 莱卡特 那个
Dialogue: 0,0:35:59.74,0:36:01.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就让我见识一下吧
Dialogue: 0,0:36:08.25,0:36:10.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这里危险 请快点回去
Dialogue: 0,0:36:10.76,0:36:13.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,您说什么呢 您才应该赶快…
Dialogue: 0,0:36:13.89,0:36:16.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,您还没回去 我们怎么能回去
Dialogue: 0,0:36:33.15,0:36:34.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这武器真适合你啊
Dialogue: 0,0:36:36.02,0:36:36.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大叔
Dialogue: 0,0:36:38.99,0:36:39.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你还活着啊
Dialogue: 0,0:36:40.10,0:36:41.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:36:41.14,0:36:42.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我去叫人救你吧
Dialogue: 0,0:36:42.62,0:36:45.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个就不必了 倒是小子你…
Dialogue: 0,0:36:46.17,0:36:47.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快找个地方藏起来吧
Dialogue: 0,0:36:48.43,0:36:50.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,城里现在到处是敌人
Dialogue: 0,0:36:50.07,0:36:50.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:37:02.64,0:37:05.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是 怎么这么难搞
Dialogue: 0,0:37:12.14,0:37:13.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,上校
Dialogue: 0,0:37:17.35,0:37:19.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很遗憾我只能送到这里了
Dialogue: 0,0:37:19.52,0:37:20.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请您快逃吧
Dialogue: 0,0:37:20.52,0:37:21.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦？
Dialogue: 0,0:37:21.19,0:37:25.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我来打倒这个家伙 请您无论如何要活下去
Dialogue: 0,0:37:25.31,0:37:25.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,上校…
Dialogue: 0,0:37:25.82,0:37:26.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快走！
Dialogue: 0,0:37:35.04,0:37:35.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这家伙
Dialogue: 0,0:37:41.49,0:37:42.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,得意忘形
Dialogue: 0,0:37:55.11,0:37:55.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,娜尔维
Dialogue: 0,0:37:56.64,0:37:57.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,洛金
Dialogue: 0,0:37:58.49,0:37:59.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不住了
Dialogue: 0,0:38:00.31,0:38:01.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这厮让我来动手
Dialogue: 0,0:38:17.05,0:38:17.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好重
Dialogue: 0,0:38:17.74,0:38:18.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,奈尔哥
Dialogue: 0,0:38:18.75,0:38:19.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别再磨磨蹭蹭的了
Dialogue: 0,0:38:20.06,0:38:21.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,第二城墙已经被突破了
Dialogue: 0,0:38:22.28,0:38:22.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:38:23.13,0:38:24.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,奈尔
Dialogue: 0,0:38:25.27,0:38:27.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我之前跟那厮有笔账要算
Dialogue: 0,0:38:27.66,0:38:29.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在已经算清了
Dialogue: 0,0:38:29.33,0:38:30.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你…
Dialogue: 0,0:38:30.11,0:38:31.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,洛金 后面
Dialogue: 0,0:38:34.63,0:38:35.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:38:37.97,0:38:39.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下次一定做个了断
Dialogue: 0,0:38:50.75,0:38:52.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,西琼大人 您没事就…
Dialogue: 0,0:38:52.13,0:38:53.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请把我放在这
Dialogue: 0,0:38:53.19,0:38:53.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是…
Dialogue: 0,0:38:54.20,0:38:56.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,帝尔锋需要我的指示
Dialogue: 0,0:38:56.43,0:38:57.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,关闭第一外门
Dialogue: 0,0:39:35.17,0:39:38.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没放手么 真执着啊
Dialogue: 0,0:39:47.46,0:39:49.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你说啥呢
Dialogue: 0,0:40:23.46,0:40:24.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,莱卡特
Dialogue: 0,0:40:24.52,0:40:29.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如波尔库斯将军这样见多识广 都对那武器出乎意料呢
Dialogue: 0,0:40:30.33,0:40:32.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,您这是要干什么啊 霍兹尔陛下
Dialogue: 0,0:40:32.14,0:40:33.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请您快回去
Dialogue: 0,0:40:34.23,0:40:36.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,干什么呢 还不快去拿伞
Dialogue: 0,0:40:36.78,0:40:37.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大臣
Dialogue: 0,0:40:37.54,0:40:38.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在
Dialogue: 0,0:40:38.83,0:40:42.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,莱卡特 无能者在战斗
Dialogue: 0,0:40:43.99,0:40:45.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为了国家在战斗
Dialogue: 0,0:40:47.74,0:40:51.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,同敌军大将战斗 操纵着未知的格雷姆
Dialogue: 0,0:40:52.06,0:40:53.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,命令他的是我
Dialogue: 0,0:40:54.80,0:40:59.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 不是命令他 是请求他
Dialogue: 0,0:41:00.07,0:41:04.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他想拒绝就可以拒绝 可莱卡特他拿起了剑
Dialogue: 0,0:41:05.09,0:41:07.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,用那双没有魔力的手
Dialogue: 0,0:41:10.89,0:41:14.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,区区淋雨这点小事 何足挂齿啊
Dialogue: 0,0:41:14.92,0:41:16.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,您说什么呢
Dialogue: 0,0:41:31.21,0:41:33.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我看到这武器的极限在哪里了
Dialogue: 0,0:41:36.63,0:41:39.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,韧带居然锤炼得如此结实
Dialogue: 0,0:42:03.91,0:42:04.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,莱卡特
Dialogue: 0,0:42:05.64,0:42:06.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,西琼大人
Dialogue: 0,0:42:06.89,0:42:07.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,放开我
Dialogue: 0,0:42:07.63,0:42:08.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行
Dialogue: 0,0:42:14.45,0:42:17.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快现身 你到底是从哪里来的
Dialogue: 0,0:42:18.17,0:42:20.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快给我看看你的真面目
Dialogue: 0,0:43:00.79,0:43:01.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太慢了
Dialogue: 0,0:43:22.97,0:43:24.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,黑银
Dialogue: 0,0:43:54.17,0:43:58.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蕾妲 弦乐大赛伊奥肯定会去的
Dialogue: 0,0:44:49.01,0:44:51.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那一日 正午稍前
Dialogue: 0,0:44:52.34,0:44:55.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,波尔库斯将军战死的消息传到大队
Dialogue: 0,0:44:55.87,0:44:58.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,波尔库斯军暂时撤退了
Dialogue: 0,0:44:59.71,0:45:05.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这条消息也立即传到了本国的罗奇斯书记长处
Dialogue: 0,0:45:08.72,0:45:09.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,克莱欧？！
Dialogue: 0,0:45:09.59,0:45:11.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的 她还活着
Dialogue: 0,0:45:11.62,0:45:15.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有消息说在毗傩天攻略战中曾目击到她
Dialogue: 0,0:45:16.05,0:45:16.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在情况怎么样？
Dialogue: 0,0:45:17.29,0:45:19.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在还不清楚
Dialogue: 0,0:45:19.22,0:45:20.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去找她吧
Dialogue: 0,0:45:21.54,0:45:23.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么也不能置之不理对吧
Dialogue: 0,0:45:24.03,0:45:25.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,您的腿…
Dialogue: 0,0:45:25.80,0:45:28.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已经不要紧了 我去和家兄商量一下
Dialogue: 0,0:45:28.67,0:45:30.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你能跟我来吗
Dialogue: 0,0:45:30.27,0:45:31.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,当然
Dialogue: 0,0:45:31.80,0:45:32.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,亲爱的
Dialogue: 0,0:45:34.12,0:45:35.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我去去就回
Dialogue: 0,0:45:42.88,0:45:44.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,娜尔维 我说你冷静下
Dialogue: 0,0:45:46.29,0:45:49.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么 托尔将军他…这是为什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:45:50.19,0:45:53.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这也是没办法的事 没办法啊
Dialogue: 0,0:45:55.98,0:45:57.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,人都死了…
Dialogue: 0,0:45:58.59,0:45:59.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,娜尔维
Dialogue: 0,0:46:05.56,0:46:06.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,洛金
Dialogue: 0,0:46:08.75,0:46:10.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真让人悲伤啊
Dialogue: 0,0:46:18.99,0:46:19.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能站起来吗
Dialogue: 0,0:46:19.87,0:46:22.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 没事 我能走
Dialogue: 0,0:46:26.22,0:46:27.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,莱卡特
Dialogue: 0,0:46:27.17,0:46:28.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我回来了
Dialogue: 0,0:46:28.67,0:46:29.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,诶？
Dialogue: 0,0:46:30.19,0:46:31.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,照约定
Dialogue: 0,0:46:37.71,0:46:40.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还没有结束对吧
Dialogue: 0,0:46:41.17,0:46:42.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,莱卡特
Dialogue: 0,0:46:43.80,0:46:47.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,杰斯那家伙还会再来对吧
Dialogue: 0,0:46:54.85,0:47:00.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大概…还要继续战斗吧
Dialogue: 0,0:47:02.87,0:47:03.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哥
Dialogue: 0,0:47:04.79,0:47:07.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,坐在这上面的就是你吗
Dialogue: 0,0:47:07.22,0:47:10.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雷加茨 你没事啊
Dialogue: 0,0:47:10.91,0:47:12.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么没事啊
Dialogue: 0,0:47:12.59,0:47:16.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你老也不回家 我这不是来找你了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:47:18.80,0:47:20.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说了句去王都就走了
Dialogue: 0,0:47:22.60,0:47:24.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你看你都干了些什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:47:25.61,0:47:28.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在这儿是干什么啊
